We recommend that the Municipal Solid Waste Management Board, through the SWM Focal Person, undertake the following:
13. Initiate the compliance of the recommended modifications on the SWMP which is to update the Municipal Ordinance on SWM pursuant to R.A 9003 and other related laws and regulations;
14. establish Materials Recovery Facility in 7 barangays to ensure approval of the plan by the National Solid Waste Management Commission and in order to facilitate the segregation of solid waste at the barangay level;
15. Hire additional manpower who will be assigned primarily in the collection of garbage and make sure that all barangays accessible by the garbage truck will be regularly collected;
16. Coordinate and require all barangays located in the mountainous areas to have a proper solid waste management and closely monitor their implementation.
